Press Releases.Title: Minister of Health Mr Ong Ye Kung to Visit Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
Press Releases.MainContent:
1.     Mr Ong Ye Kung, Minister for Health, will make a working visit to Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia, from 23 to 25 March 2022, at the invitation of Minister of Health of Malaysia, Yang Berhormat Tuan Khairy Jamaluddin.

2.     Mr Ong will meet with other political leaders in Malaysia during the trip. He will also visit the National Institutes of Health on 24 March, where he will deliver a keynote address.

3.     He will be accompanied by senior officials from the Ministry of Health.

MINISTRY OF HEALTH

22 MARCH 2022
